quran[28]{c,v,t}:
  69,35,"Giɗo ɓadondiraaɗo alanaamo Ñalnde Darngal, ko duñanamo lette ɗen."
  69,36,"Wanaa ñaametee woodani mo, si wanaa ko siiɓaa e ɓalli yimɓe Yiite ɓen."
  69,37,"Hay gooto ñaametee ndin ƴiƴƴiƴiri, si wanaa yedduɓe e bakkondimɓe ɓen."
  69,38,"Allah woondirii ko yi'oton kon."
  69,39,"O woondiri kadi ko on yi'ataa kon."
  69,40,"Pellet, Alqur'aana ko daalol Allah, ngol O Nulaaɗo Makko tedduɗo on janngata e dow mon."
  69,41,"Wanaa nde konnguɗi yimoowo; tawde nde yuɓɓiraaka wa gimɗi. Kono fanɗii ko gomɗinton."
  69,42,"Nde wanaa kadi nde konnguɗi mbileejo, tawde mbilewu hino seedi e Alqur'aana. Kono fanɗii ko waajitotoɗon."
  69,43,"Ko jippiniraande ka Jeyɗo tageefo ngon fow."
  69,44,"Si tawno Muhammadu fefindino e Amen yoga e konnguɗi ɗi iwraani e Amen."
  69,45,"Ko pellet, Men yoɓtotono bmo, Men naangira mo doole e kattal."
  69,46,"Hooti Men taƴayno e makko ɗaɗol yottiingol e ɓernde nden."
  69,47,"Alaa hay gooto e mo'on haɗoowo e makko, himo daɗndii e fefindagol e Amen fii mon."
  69,48,"Pellet, Alqur'aana ko waaju hulirooɓe Joomi mun ɓen ɗoftagol yamiraaɗi Makko ɗin, e woɗɗitoo haɗaaɗi Makko ɗin."
  69,49,"Haray kadi, Meɗen anndi fennooɓe ndee Alqur'aanaare ina e mon."
  69,50,"Pellet non, fennugol Alqur'aana ngol, ko nimse mawɗe wonoyta Ñalnde Darngal."
  69,51,"Pellet kadi, Alqur'aana ko goonga yananaaɗo mo sikke alaa e mu'un, wonnde ko ka Allah nde iwri."
  69,52,"Haray an Nulaaɗo, subbunhinor innde Joomi maa, kala ko haandaani e Makko, jantoɗaa innde Joomi maa Mawɗo On."
  70,1,"Gooto e sirkooɓe ɓen toranike e hoore mun e yimɓe mun ɓen lette, himo jalkita, sikkugol lette ɗen waɗaatah. Hara ɗum waɗay Ñalnde Darngal."
  70,2,"Wonannde yedduɓe Allah ɓen, alah duñanoowo ɓe ɗee lette."
  70,3,"Ko immorde ka Allha, Jom toowal e darja, e ɓure e neemaaji."
  70,4,"Malaa'ika'en wonndude e Jibriilu hino e ƴawa e ɗin darjaaji Ñalnde Darngal, juutungal, eɓɓirtengal duuɓi ujune cappanɗe jowi."
  70,5,"Muñño tun, yo Nulaaɗo, muñal ngal jillah ɗenƴagol maa wullitagol."
  70,6,"Kamɓe hiɓe reeni ɗee lette ko woɗɗiiɗe tultooje."
  70,7,"Menen le Meɗen reeni ɗe ko ɓadiiɗe, yanayɗe feere mun alaa."
  70,8,"Ñalnde kammu ngun wa'oyta wano sila maa kaŋŋe taayinaaɗum."
  70,9,"Pelle ɗen kadi wa'oya wano hottollo goobaako saraako."
  70,10,"Ka ɓadondiraaɗo lamdotaako fii musiɗɗo mun, tawde haray mo kala hino sokliri hoore mun."